Be aware the S&P 500 was up only 0.4% during the #Dow 10-day win streak and only 6 days out of the 10 where higher.
The #Dow 10-day win streak is over. Worth noting, since 1896 this was the 17th 10-day win streak. Up 2.8% these 10 days is the weakest ever.
If green today, the #Dow is up 11 in a row. Would be 2nd time this yr up 11 in row. Since 1896, that has never happened twice in a yr.
If #Dow ends in positive territory today - it will mark TEN straight days of record closes for the 36th record close this year -TR
